Dive:    https://github.com/wagoodman/dive
wget https://github.com/wagoodman/dive/releases/download/v0.9.1/dive_0.9.1_linux_amd64.deb
sudo apt install ./dive_0.9.1_linux_amd64.deb
dive <your-image-tag>


